# User Guide for Creating a Training Room

_By Nadezhda_

---

## Steps to Create the Training Room

1. Go to the **Battle!** menu and select **Team Training**.  
2. Click **Create Room**. A **Training Room** window will appear. Use this window to configure your room.  
3. Select a **map** from the list. The selected map will be shown on the right.  
4. Specify the **duration** of the battle.  
5. (Optional) Check **By Invitation** to make the room accessible only to invited players.  
6. Write a **short description** (for example: skills to be practiced).  
7. Click **Create**. The room will be created, and you will see the training room screen.  
---
